name: Sugar Skull large slouch bag
description: This slouch bag is hand made, with black Alexander Henry sugar skull fabric outer, and red cotton inside, and for the strap.  The closure is a strap with a magnetic closure.  I also am able to make this bag in the red sugar skull fabric, so message me!!  As always, I welcome custom orders, so if you don’t see it here, just ask and you will receive!!!!!

name: Sacred Heart slouch bag
description: This slouch bag is made with the Alexander Henry sacred heart fabric on the outside, and a white cotton inside and strap. description: This is a set of 2 medium size bows on medium barrettes.  The inside springs can be removed for thicker hair. If you don’t see something that you like, message me, I love custom orders!!  Ask and you will receive!!

name: Skullerfly Barrettes
description: I have these in red, green, blue, pink, yellow, and orange colors.  The skullerflies are mounted on small french barrettes, and the spring insert can be remover for thicker hair.  They have landed on a thin strip of leopard print ribbon.  Price is for a set of 2.  Please specify what color you would like.
